---
// src/components/NewSiteBanner.astro
---

<section class="banner-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="banner-content">
      <h2 class="banner-title">¡Nos cambiamos de web!</h2>
      <p class="banner-text">Nuestra web se ha movido a <a href="https://delegados.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">delegados.vercel.app</a>. Es la nueva web unificada para todos los delegados del centro. <br> A partir de la próxima semana esta web redirigirá a la nueva. ¡Nos vemos!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="banner-action">
      <a href="https://delegados.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">Visitar nueva web</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.banner-section {
  padding: 40px 0;
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #001e60, #003d99);
  color: white;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 20px;
}

.banner-content {
  text-align: left;
}

.banner-title {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.banner-text {
  font-size: 1.125rem;
  font-weight: 400;
  max-width: 600px;
}

.banner-text a {
  color: #90cdf4;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.banner-action {
  text-align: right;
}

.btn-primary {
  padding: 16px 32px;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  transform-style: preserve-3d;
  background: white;
  color: #001e60;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
}

.btn-primary:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) rotateX(10deg);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .container {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .banner-content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .banner-action {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
}
</style>
